This paper focuses on optimizing the execution of Deep Neural Networks (DNNs) on mobile devices, specifically for real-time video stream processing. This topic is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE), as DNNs are a key building block of these fields. Additionally, the paper mentions architecture-aware optimization, which could fall under the category of computer architecture (cs.AR).
